
This Python package provides the module 'beatadjoint' -- beatadjoint
is a problem and solver collection for cardiac electrophysiology
models.

Installation:
-------------

See separate file ./INSTALL for how to install the module and a list
of dependencies.

Documentation:
---------------

Update the API documentation for beatadjoint by running the script:

    ./scripts/generate-doc

The full API documentation for beatadjoint can also be automatically
generated. Generate the full documentation, including new
configuration files etc, by running the script:

    ./scripts/generate-full-doc

assuming that beatadjoint and the optional dependency Sphinx
(sphinx-doc.org) is installed.

